Have you ever gotten frustrated when trying to comment back on Instagram. 
Typing people's @handles can take so much time...and then there's auto-correct. 
So annoying...

Watch the video above to learn how to save time when replying to comments on your image.

And remember to check out http://socialdraft.com/ 

It's a social media scheduling tool and calendar where you can schedule posts to Instagram, search by hashtag, like posts, and re-post to not just Instagram, but also to Facebook, Twitter, LinkedIn and Pinterest....but it does even more than that, so check it out.